---
// Pipeline de assinatura da NF-e (perfil SEFAZ): assina o <infNFe> por Id.
interface Props {
  lang?: 'pt' | 'en';
}
const { lang = 'pt' } = Astro.props;

const t = {
  pt: {
    steps: [
      { n: 1, title: 'Montar a NF-e', desc: '<infNFe Id="NFe3106…"> com os dados fiscais' },
      { n: 2, title: 'Canonicalizar o <infNFe>', desc: 'C14N inclusiva: qualquer byte fora do padrão invalida a assinatura' },
      { n: 3, title: 'Digest do elemento', desc: 'SHA-1 do canonicalizado → <DigestValue>, referenciado pelo Id (#NFe3106…)' },
      { n: 4, title: 'Assinar o <SignedInfo>', desc: 'transforms: enveloped-signature + C14N; RSA-SHA1 com a chave A1 (ICP-Brasil) → <SignatureValue>' },
      { n: 5, title: 'Embutir a <Signature>', desc: 'irmã do <infNFe>, com o <X509Certificate> do emitente' },
    ],
    caption:
      'O passo 2 é onde quase todo mundo sangra: a SEFAZ rejeita a nota se a canonicalização não bater byte a byte. A API sign_element_by_id encapsula os cinco passos.',
  },
  en: {
    steps: [
      { n: 1, title: 'Build the invoice', desc: '<infNFe Id="NFe3106…"> with the fiscal data' },
      { n: 2, title: 'Canonicalize <infNFe>', desc: 'inclusive C14N: a single off-spec byte invalidates the signature' },
      { n: 3, title: 'Digest the element', desc: 'SHA-1 of the canonical form → <DigestValue>, referenced by Id (#NFe3106…)' },
      { n: 4, title: 'Sign <SignedInfo>', desc: 'transforms: enveloped-signature + C14N; RSA-SHA1 with the A1 key (ICP-Brasil) → <SignatureValue>' },
      { n: 5, title: 'Embed <Signature>', desc: 'sibling of <infNFe>, carrying the issuer <X509Certificate>' },
    ],
    caption:
      'Step 2 is where most people bleed: SEFAZ rejects the invoice if canonicalization does not match byte for byte. The sign_element_by_id API wraps the five steps.',
  },
}[lang];
---

<figure class="not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-md flex-col items-stretch text-sm">
    {
      t.steps.map((s, i) => (
        <>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg px-4 py-2.5">
            <span class="mr-2 font-mono text-xs text-accent">{s.n}</span>
            <span class="font-medium text-fg">{s.title}</span>
            <p class="mt-0.5 text-xs text-muted">{s.desc}</p>
          </div>
          {i < t.steps.length - 1 && (
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center py-1 text-muted" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="h-3 w-px bg-border" />
              <span class="text-[10px] leading-none">▼</span>
            </div>
          )}
        </>
      ))
    }
  </div>
  <figcaption class="mt-4 text-center text-xs text-muted">{t.caption}</figcaption>
</figure>
